    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>pastry</strong> into triangles, roughly the size of your palm</p>",
      "order": 5,
