    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cheesy leek & potato mixture</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top the mixture with the <strong>pastry triangles</strong>, leaving some gaps in between and brush with a little <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>cheesy leek, potato & mustard pie</strong></p>",
